{"tid":1547026,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[和理非行動] 教你點做陪審員","createTime":"2019-09-06T13:55:29.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-26T11:28:57.000Z","uid":8948,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"b0ed3d3596c1ce65f85c85e470deb0130f56623e","tid":1547026,"uid":8948,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T13:55:29.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">全民陪審團！正式啟動！一人一信做陪審員！</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n１。陪審員資格<br />\n- <span style=\"color: gold;\">年滿21歲</span>但未滿65歲；<br />\n- 精神健全而並無任何使其不能出任陪審員的情況如聽覺或視覺的損傷等；品格良好，及<br />\n- 熟悉聆訊時所採用的語言&mdash; 即中文<span style=\"color: gold;\">或</span>英文（視乎個別情況而定）<br />\n<br />\n2。登記方法<br />\n寄一封申請信去入境處<br />\n<br />\n寄送地址： 香港灣仔告士打道7號入境事務大樓12樓行政主任（人事登記）支援組收<br />\n所需文件：<br />\n 1）學歷證明副本<br />\n2）已填妥之ROP 18表格<br />\n<br />\n信內所需資料 <br />\n1）申請人中英文姓名<br />\n2）香港身份證號碼<br />\n3）聯絡電話<br />\n4）簽名<br />\n<br />\n信件template, copy去Word度再改資料就印得<br />\n&quot;To whom it may concern,<br />\n<br />\nI would like to express my desire to serve as a member of the jury. <br />\n<br />\nI am a permanent resident of Hong Kong (HKID: xxxxx)) who was born and raised in Hong Kong. Having graduated from the University of xxx, I possess an excellent command in the English language. <br />\n<br />\nAttached herewith copies of my credentials for your information. I would be grateful if you could add my name into the pool of members for jury service.<br />\n<br />\nBest Regards,<br />\n中文姓名<br />\n英文姓名<br />\n身份證號碼<br />\n聯絡電話<br />\n<br />\n個人簽名<br />\n<br />\nEncl.<br />\n1. copy of HKID card<br />\n2. copy of university certificate from the University of xxx&quot;<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nROP18: <a href=\"https://www.immd.gov.hk/pdforms/rop18.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.immd.gov.hk%2Fpdforms%2Frop18.pdf&d=ICpLbNdPoidNzy8g%2B0GH2uIUDtzVwJRUTDGgxy4aIpc%3D&h=66b65cb4\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.immd.gov.hk/pdforms/rop18.pdf</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">FAQ ／ 懶人包 </span></span><br />\n1。我已經21歲以上，hd／asso 畢業可唔可以申請？<br />\nA：可以，但你需要寄封信俾入境處，cover letter ＋ ROP18 ＋ 學歷副本（畢業證書）以<br />\n<br />\n2。我仲係學生可唔可以申請？<br />\nA：如果仲係學生既話係做唔到陪審員。但你可以做既係叫身邊既人都去申請同埋幫手推post。<br />\n<br />\n同埋同我查定讀音背咗佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://topick.hket.com/article/1619319/女陪審員宣誓不懂讀「almighty」即被DQ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftopick.hket.com%2Farticle%2F1619319%2F%E5%A5%B3%E9%99%AA%E5%AF%A9%E5%93%A1%E5%AE%A3%E8%AA%93%E4%B8%8D%E6%87%82%E8%AE%80%E3%80%8Calmighty%E3%80%8D%E5%8D%B3%E8%A2%ABDQ&d=ICpLbNdPoidNzy8g%2B0GH2uIUDtzVwJRUTDGgxy4aIpc%3D&h=cc8b4c7a\" target=\"_blank\">https://topick.hket.com/article/1619319/女陪審員宣誓不懂讀「almighty」即被DQ</a><br />\n耶：I swear by Almighty God that I will faithfully try the defendant(s) and give a true verdict(s) according to the evidence.<br />\n非耶：I do solemnly, sincerely, and truly declare that I will hearken to the evidence, and a true verdict give, to the best of my skill and knowledge, without fear, favour, or affection.<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">謹記煲底之約。願榮光歸香港。<br />\n光復香港，時代革命。</span></span><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=y7yRDOLCy4Y\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3Dy7yRDOLCy4Y&d=ICpLbNdPoidNzy8g%2B0GH2uIUDtzVwJRUTDGgxy4aIpc%3D&h=74b385dc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=y7yRDOLCy4Y</a>"},{"pid":"a61d77ce1aee438eedba71b0778c0e814ebe7bce","tid":1547026,"uid":290761,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T13:56:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/A8vAmVU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FA8vAmVU.jpg&h=305